    "attributes": {
        "action": "5-year prison sentences and communications restrictions for child sex offenders",
        "additional_details": "I believe too many child sex offenders receive non-custodial sentences, and are not subject to restrictions that could help prevent reoffending.\r\n \r\nI want stricter sentences to be set out in law, and mandatory lifelong restrictions on communicating with children, to help prevent reoffending.\r\n",
        "background": "I want a minimum custodial sentence of at least 5 years for any sexual offence toward a child, with lifelong restrictions on communicating with children, and mandatory higher sentences for repeat offenders.",
